# AI Pack assets directory.
#
# This file exists to keep the directory in git so AGP's
# :app:assetPackReleasePreBundleTask does not fail with
# "path does not exist" when the model artifacts are absent locally.
#
# The content of this .gitkeep is INTENTIONALLY IDENTICAL across all
# three AI Pack modules (:gemma_model, :gemma_embed_model,
# :paddleocr_model). bundletool's EntryClashValidator rejects entries
# at the same relative path that differ in byte content, and an asset
# pack's .gitkeep would otherwise clash. Per-pack documentation lives
# in the module's README.md (one level up).

